text: small congregation but great worship and Pastor Dennis Lee does some great preaching of the Gospel of Jesus . He has a good lineup of guest preachers and i have heard some wonderful preaching there from Ed Delph and Samuel manohan. lukas and bob fits have performed there as well
A very cosy family-oriented church. Filled with fantastic worship and awesome sermon messages.

A place of encounter...
A place where the Presence of God dwells.
Everything will live where the River flows!
Incredible worship and fellowship. Come and be blessed!
